                        <p>		UHD 4K (3840 x 2160)30fps, Slowmotion 240fps  </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-3 col-md-3 pb-product-details-fa">
                        <span class="fa fa-microchip fa-lg"></span>
                        <h4><strong>4GB RAM</strong></h4>
                        <p>	Exynos 9611 </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-3 col-md-3 pb-product-details-fa">
